$ link /SUBSYSTEM

The `/SUBSYSTEM` option specifies the → Windows/development/Visual-Studio/link/subsystem[subsystem] of the resulting executable or
→ Windows/development/Portable-Executable/DLL[dll].

Depending on the chosen subsystem, the linker chooses an entrypoint (which can be overwritten with → Windows/development/Visual-Studio/link/options/entry[/ENTRY]).
